item.title: NRL 360 : Milford challenged by Bennett after being dropped for Round 1, Roosters ask for Salary Cap relief and Moses on the move? - 28/02/2023
item.description:
Catch up on all the Rugby League news from NRL360, Tuesday the 28th of February, with host Braith Anasta and of course, Paul Kent.

The boys are joined by Paul Crawley and Dave Riccio to chat through the decision by veteran coach Wayne Bennett to drop five-eight Anthony Milford ahead of their first game with the Sydney Roosters. The boys also look into the Eastern Suburbs side asking for salary cap relief and look into if Mitchell Moses future lies with the Eels...
